      <title>鳥のくちばしに似た「貝」…歯ごたえのある甘い冬の珍味 - 韓国忠清南道洪城郡</title>
      <link>https://codecorea.github.io/posts/the-shellfish-that-resembles-a-birds-beak-chewy-and-sweet-winter-delicacy-280-ja/</link>
