&lt;div data-address=&#34;Hongseong-gun, Chungcheongnam-do, Korea&#34; data-title=&#34;the-shellfish-that-resembles-a-birds-beak-chewy-and-sweet-winter-delicacy--280&#34; id=&#34;content&#34;&gt;
 &lt;div class=&#34;img_typeBox typeFix clfix&#34;&gt;
